STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Wally NANCE, a/k/a Willey Nance, Defendant-Petitioner. C-95 September Term 2018
080879 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 28, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001493-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
